<item>
            <title>[LU-4870] LFSCK3: Race between layout LFSCK and metadata migration</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4870</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to current metadata migration implementation, before the old MDT-object is removed, both the new MDT-object and old MDT-object will reference the same LOV layout. Then if the layout LFSCK finds the new MDT-object by race, it will regard related OST-object(s) as multiple referenced case, and will try to create new OST-object(s) for the new MDT-object.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
